{"tid":1562822,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯：不簽回尼馬不失望","createTime":"2019-09-12T07:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T11:39:24.000Z","uid":210711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"70de3451202893e7474232a305a43c338b54ef13","tid":1562822,"uid":210711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:16:10.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】巴塞隆拿球星美斯坦言不知道會方有沒有全力簽尼馬，但坦言對交易泡湯不感失望。<br />\n巴塞隆拿今夏邀請尼馬回巢的轉會肥皂劇最後化泡影，一直有指球王美斯（Lionel Messi）不滿會方不著緊，及至日前，他終首度為此開腔，「我很希望尼馬能回來，説實話，我不知道巴塞隆拿是否竭盡全力去簽，但巴黎聖日耳門從來不是容易對付的談判對手。」 <br />\n對於老友沒能重返魯營球場，美斯表示不失望：「我對此不感到失望，我們有出色的陣容，足以應付不同賽事，沒尼馬同樣能做到。尼馬是世上最出色球員之一，有他的商業影響力，球會的整體影響力會有所提高。」 <br />\n美斯最後還否認球員推動會方簽回尼馬，「大家沒要求把尼馬買回來，我們只是提出自己的意見而已。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF-%E4%B8%8D%E7%B0%BD%E5%9B%9E%E5%B0%BC%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B-031951963--spt.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2596%25AF-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%259C%259B-031951963--spt.html&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=490c9a79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF-%E4%B8%8D%E7%B0%BD%E5%9B%9E%E5%B0%BC%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B-031951963--spt.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"cfa2b34f4c37f61348aef2019f14ddd0fe8d3f55","tid":1562822,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: c